# Environment variables for the Allen Kenoyer Glass rebuild.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values for local development.
# `.env.local` is git-ignored — never commit it.
#
# Phase 0 has no required env vars yet. Variables are added here as they
# are introduced in later phases (e.g., Supabase URL/keys in Phase 2,
# Resend API key in Phase 3, ESP key in Phase 3, analytics in Phase 4).
